import { Box, Button, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

const SecondPage = () => {
  return (
    <Box>
      <Box sx={{display:'flex',flexDirection:'row',justifyContent:'space-between'}}>
        <Typography variant='h6'>Popular Health Checkup Packages</Typography>
         <Button variant='outlined'  sx={{color:'#2CCE6C'}}>Compare Packages</Button>
         <Button variant='outlined' color='success'>Create Your Package</Button>
         <Button variant='outlined' color='success'>View All Package</Button>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default SecondPage
